Package algorithms.compression_algorithms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Compresser
    This interface defines what each Compresser has to do.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommonCompresser
    This class should contain what's common to all compressers.
    Demo  
    FixedBitSet
    This class is the original BitSet fixed - wrapped with a size field.
    Hchar
    This class is a helper in the HuffmanAlg class - it saves the char with its count in the text and its binary representation - as FixedBitSet.
    HuffmanAlg
    This class features the Huffman Compresser.
    HuffmanDictionary
    A dictionary mapping between characters and Hchars.
    HuffmanReader
    BONUS - This class reads Compressed data from a Reader and returns the data.
    HuffmanWriter
    BONUS - This class writes compressed huffman data to a writer.
    WordDictionary
    This class can compress and decompress data by the naive dictionary methods.
